title: Mystery shrouding oldest animal fossils solved

title_detail.value: Mystery shrouding oldest animal fossils solved

summary: Scientists have discovered that 558 million-year-old Dickinsonia fossils do not reveal all of the features of the earliest known animals, which potentially had mouths and guts.
